Package se.itu.hunt

Class GridPosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.itu.hunt.Position
      • se.itu.hunt.GridPosition

  • public class GridPosition
extends Position

    Represents an immutable Position to be used in a JTable.

    Note that a JTable has (0,0) in the upper left corner.

    Since Swing uses a method getValueAt(int row, int col), we'll swap the x and y values in the call to super().
